1 (3) THE DATE OF REPAIR; AND
2 (4) THE ESTIMATED WATER LOSS.
3 (B) EACH DEPARTMENT SHALL UPDATE ANY INFORMATION PUBLISHED ON
4 ITS WEBSITE UNDER SUBSECTION (A) OF THIS SECTION WITHIN 30 DAYS AFTER ANY
5 ACTION TAKEN IN RELATION TO A WATER MAIN BREAK OR LEAK.
6 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
7 October 1, 2025.

